metadata.abstract: This document outlines the Letter of Agreement (LoA) between vACC Germany and V-NATO, detailing the procedures and protocols for military operations within the VATSIM Germany network. It includes information on the coordination and communication between VATSIM Germany and Virtual NATO (VNATO) entities. The document is essential for controllers and pilots involved in military operations, providing guidelines to ensure smooth and efficient handling of military traffic. Key elements include the responsibilities of each party, the communication channels to be used, and specific procedures for various military scenarios. This agreement aims to enhance the cooperation and operational efficiency between civilian and military aviation within the VATSIM network.
